\intbl \ql \b Background\b0 \line The South Africa College of Applied Psychology \'28SACAP\'29 is registered with the Department of Higher Education and Training and is accredited to offer higher education programmes by the HEQC. The institution is currently offering a Diploma in Counselling Communication and a Graduate Diploma in Counselling. The institution submitted two related programmes\'2C this Higher Certificate and an Advanced Certificate\'2C for offering in contact mode of delivery. The Higher Certificate in Counselling and Communication Skills was tabled at the AC meeting of the 01 June 2011\'2C and the committee recommended that the proposed programme be accredited with prior to commencement conditions whereas the Advanced Certificate was deferred. This application is for the distance mode of delivery.\line \cell \pard 

